#Kembrya

![A photo documenting Kembrya's first movie in the park, featuring the movie 'Almost Famous'.](https://scontent-ord1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xfa1/v/t1.0-9/11813511_870702259691172_7035772613638210585_n.jpg?oh=b771f213aadcbe78a0ab7d639808478a&oe=563AF871" style="float:right;width:500px;height:400px;).
		
			#About
Kembrya has been an advocate for human rights since she was able to observe 
and understand. Born October 5th, 1998 she is a hardcore libra enthusiast!
She can often be found researching (fake) zodiacs (on Tumblr), watching Netflix, reading a book, 
touching up on social issues, chilling, or spending time with the ones she 
love most. She has a small circle of friends and a large crowd of associates, but
she loves everyone she's come in contact with because everything happens for a 
reason.   
		
Interest involve marching band, pep band, and concert band. 
Theater tech, book club, impact club, SAAD, and Girls Who Code (GWC) has taken up 
a lot of time out of her life this past year. She also volunteers for show
choir crew to help keep the fine arts program running efficiently.
